originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_name, 
    SUM(l.l_quantity) AS total_quantity, 
    AVG(l.l_extendedprice) AS avg_price, 
    CONCAT('Total Quantity: ', CAST(SUM(l.l_quantity) AS CHAR), 
           ', Avg Price: ', CAST(AVG(l.l_extendedprice) AS DECIMAL(10, 2))) AS summary,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    c.c_name AS customer_name
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON c.c_custkey = l.l_orderkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    p.p_name LIKE '%widget%'
    AND l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1996-01-01' AND '1996-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, r.r_name, n.n_name, s.s_name, c.c_name
ORDER BY 
    total_quantity DESC, avg_price ASC
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."p_name", "t4"."p_name") AS "P_NAME", "t4"."TOTAL_QUANTITY", "t4"."AVG_PRICE", CONCAT('Total Quantity: ', CAST("t4"."TOTAL_QUANTITY" AS CHAR(1)), ', Avg Price: ', CAST(CAST("t4"."AVG_PRICE" AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) AS VARCHAR)) AS "SUMMARY", "t4"."REGION_NAME", "t4"."NATION_NAME", "t4"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t4"."CUSTOMER_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."p_name", "s1"."r_name", "nation"."n_name", "supplier"."s_name", "customer"."c_name", SUM("t0"."l_quantity") AS "TOTAL_QUANTITY", AVG("t0"."l_extendedprice") AS "AVG_PRICE", MIN("s1"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME", MIN("nation"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME", MIN("supplier"."s_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", MIN("customer"."c_name") AS "CUSTOMER_NAME"
FROM "customer"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31') AS "t0" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "t0"."l_orderkey"
INNER JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "nation" ON "s1"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey" INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_name" LIKE '%widget%') AS "t1" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "t1"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey") ON "t0"."l_partkey" = "t1"."p_partkey"
GROUP BY "customer"."c_name", "s1"."r_name", "nation"."n_name", "supplier"."s_name", "t1"."p_name"
ORDER BY 6 DESC NULLS FIRST, 7
LIMIT 10) AS "t4"
